CairnCMS JavaScript SDK

This package (`@cairncms/sdk`) is derived from the Directus JavaScript SDK
(https://github.com/directus/directus/tree/main/sdk), originally published as
`@directus/sdk` under the MIT License.

The original SDK source was imported from Directus v10.13.3 (the `sdk/` directory
at that tag, which shipped as `@directus/sdk@16.1.2`). Subsequent modifications,
CairnCMS-specific changes, and ongoing maintenance are attributed to the CairnCMS
project and listed in the project's git history.

